      "lineNumber": 10,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Strict \u002B literal \u002B mismatched bytes \u2192 BUILD error (not runtime).\nRequires fixture photo.png (1x1 transparent PNG). The build step itself\nmust fail with a BuildValidation error; this .test.goal is structured so\nthat the test runner sees the build failure as the success signal.\n\nThe exact test-runner shape for \u0022expects build to fail\u0022 is open; if the\nrunner doesn\u0027t have it, this test asserts via a wrapper goal that runs\nthe builder and checks the error.",
